<topic id="topic1" xml:lang="en"><title id="fa138336">gpexpand.status</title><body><p>The <codeph>gpexpand.status</codeph> table contains information about the status of a system
      expansion operation. Status for specific tables involved in the expansion is stored in <xref
        href="./gp_expansion_tables.xml#topic1" type="topic" format="dita"/>.</p><p>In a normal expansion operation it is not necessary to modify the
data stored in this table. </p><table id="fa138428"><title>gpexpand.status</title><tgroup cols="4"><colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="131pt"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="97pt"/><colspec colnum="3" colname="col3" colwidth="82pt"/><colspec colnum="4" colname="col4" colwidth="138pt"/><thead><row><entry colname="col1">column</entry><entry colname="col2">type</entry><entry colname="col3">references</entry><entry colname="col4">description</entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry colname="col1"><codeph>status</codeph></entry><entry colname="col2">text</entry><entry colname="col3"/><entry colname="col4">Tracks the status of an expansion operation. Valid values
                  are:<p><codeph>SETUP</codeph></p><p><codeph>SETUP DONE
                  </codeph></p><p><codeph>EXPANSION STARTED</codeph></p><p><codeph>EXPANSION
                  STOPPED</codeph></p><p><codeph>COMPLETED</codeph></p></entry></row><row><entry colname="col1"><codeph>updated</codeph></entry><entry colname="col2">timestamp without time zone</entry><entry colname="col3"/><entry colname="col4">Timestamp of the last change in status.</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></topic>
